    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>the problem is there is no \"new chapter.\" that's just something people say to feel better. i don't feel like i'm at a crossroads, i just feel... finished. like the story already reached its conclusion and i'm just lingering in the credits. it feels more like a heavy, permanent weight than a temporary slump. does that even make sense? like, if the spark is gone, what's actually left to build on?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
